![Episode81.jpg](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/1578270249669-BH2ME6FK383I14P40G98/Episode81.jpg)

The final season of Jessica Jones was released earlier this month, also marking the last season of Marvel Netflix shows. It continues the story of hard-boiled and super-powered P.I. Jessica Jones as she tries to navigate Hell's Kitchen and walk the tightrope of morality along the way. This time she has a serial killer hot on her trail, and a sister hell-bent on revenge, making for possibly the most emotional Jessica Jones season yet! Grab your favorite leather jacket and pour one last glass of bourbon as we take a look at the last season of Jessica Jones on Netflix  
  
If you can, please leave us a **_review_** on [**ITunes**](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience, and grow as podcasters! Rate us where ever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our merchandise! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by ComicBook Clique, the one stop for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media.  
  
